==English==
===Proper noun===
'''G-d'''

#A deliberately incomplete spelling of the proper noun '''[[God]]'''.

===Usage notes===
*'''G-d''' is used by those who believe that writing God's name in full destroys its divinity, or to advertise the writer's adherence to this belief, or to acknowledge respect for the reader's beliefs in this regard.

